 </title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/5431/how-to-output-i3-nagbar-on-a-different-monitor/?answer=5432#post-id-5432</link><description>As of [this ticket](http://github.com/i3/i3/issues/1405) the nagbar is always directed to the most left monitor. Development in progress to always show it on all outputs it can find.</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Feb 2015 13:11:38 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/5431/how-to-output-i3-nagbar-on-a-different-monitor/?answer=5432#post-id-5432</guid></item></channel></rss>